TONS LIGHTOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 3.17% to NT$87,356,000 from NT$90,213,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             87,356           90,213    
YOY%              -3.17%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            323,855          327,261    
YOY%              -1.04% 
